      <h2>5. In-App Purchases</h2>
      <p><strong>DocArmor Unlock</strong> is available as a one-time, non-consumable in-app purchase of <strong>$7.99 USD</strong> (or equivalent local currency), processed by Apple through the App Store. This unlocks premium features for your account.</p>
      <ul>
